translation.Name: Greece Note Tower Observations
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: Tuesday, 24th ~ 12 idle infected spotted wandering from the farm
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_3: Thursday, 26th ~ 4 infected attacked from across the bridge.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: Saturday, 28th ~ 7 infected spotted gathering near the farm.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_5: Monday, 30th ~ 13 infected now have gathered by the farm. We'll need to clear them out soon.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_6: Wednesday, 2nd ~ Small horde has amassed at the farm, sent out combat party. Just spotted another group across the bridge. Looks like around, 6? No. 12? No, missed a few...
